_sText: zm_siberia_v2 This is similar to the original, just expanded upon. Changes: - Fixed all bugs in the Grain Elevator - Added more snow banks and trees - Added the infamous German .88 FlaK Gun - New big house with 1 secret inside - Frozen Train - Re-did ambient lighting - Other Stuff...
